content.raw: should we just make the two `ground_plane` models the same, e.g. by removing the [collide_bitmask](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/1e71620459fa392ec1ec6a30df84d75e0086615d/models/ground_plane/model.sdf?at=default#cl-15) element in the one hosted in gazebo? we haven't really been making any changes to this model recently and I guess it's here in the gazebo repo so that  gazebo doesn't have to download it when it's launched the first time.
